<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0021', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:196'>欽定四庫全書　　　　經部一</span>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='196:213'>　紫巖易𫝊　　　　　　易𩔖</span>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='213:219'>　　提要</span>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='219:245'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案紫巖易傳十卷宋張浚撰紫巖者</span>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='245:268'>　　　　浚自號也其曽孫獻之跋云忠獻公潛心於</span>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='268:291'>　　　　易嘗為之傳前後兩著稿親題第二稿云此</span>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='291:314'>　　　　本改正處極多紹興戊寅四月六日某書始</span>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='314:337'>　　　　為定本矣獻之嘗繕録之附以讀易襍説通</span>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='337:363'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0021', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='363:386'>　　　　為十卷藏之於家據此則襍説一卷似獻之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='386:409'>　　　　所續附者然考獻之是跋在嘉定庚辰而朱</span>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='409:432'>　　　　子作浚行狀已稱有易解及襍説共十卷則</span>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='432:455'>　　　　獻之特繕録而已未嘗編次也其書立言醇</span>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='455:478'>　　　　粹凡説隂陽動静皆適於義理之正末一卷</span>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='478:501'>　　　　即所謂襍説胡一桂議其専主劉牧今觀所</span>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='501:524'>　　　　論河圖信然朱子不取牧説而作浚行狀但</span>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='524:547'>　　　　稱尤深於易春秋論孟不言其易出於牧殆</span>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='547:573'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0021', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='573:593'>　　　　諱之歟乾隆四十五年九月恭校上</span>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='593:627'>　　　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='627:654'>　　　　　　　　　總　校　官　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>　陸　費　墀</span>
</p>
